    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines the IP Flow Information eXport (IPFIX) architecture for the selective monitoring of IP Flows, and for the export of measured IP Flow information from an IPFIX Device to a Collector.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
